OL,3,CBoy in critical condition after being
OL,4,Chit by a car in west Belfast
OL,6,FAn 11-year-old boy is critically ill
OL,7,Fin hospital following a road collision
OL,8,Fin Belfast.
OL,10,FPolice said a grey BMW X5 and the
OL,11,Fchild, who was a pedestrian, were
OL,12,Finvolved in the incident in the
OL,13,FShankill Road on Saturday evening.
OL,15,FA 34-year-old man was arrested at the
OL,16,Fscene, but has since been released on
OL,17,Fbail pending further police inquiries.
