OL,3,CBoy in critical condition after being
OL,4,Chit by a car in west Belfast
OL,6,FPolice are appealing for witnesses to
OL,7,Fcome forward following the collision
OL,8,Fwhich happened close to the junction
OL,9,Fwith Boundary Street at approximately
OL,10,F7.25pm on Saturday.
